Fushimi Inari is a shy, middle school girl living in Kyoto's Fushimi ward. 
She has a crush on her classmate Tanbabashi Kouji, but cannot 
express her feelings. One day, as thanks for helping a fox pup, 
the deity Uka no Mitama no Kami grants her the ability to change her shape.

Source: ANN
